reviewText: Thisseems to just a bunch of someone's personal travel photos, in a slideshow, with site captions added. Mildly annoying or pleasant (depending on your taste) musical background track added. No narrative. No context. Seems mostly Catholic or Orthodox/Byzantine site selections. Way overpriced. No real connection to Biblical stories or cultural or historical context added, so don't wast your money if that is what you are looking for.
